## 9. ML Extension 

### 9.1 KMeans Airport Clustering (with auto-k elbow)
- **What:** cluster POIs in France using KMeans; map each cluster center to the nearest airport.
- **Why:** demonstrates an applied ML/analytics feature built on top of the engineered data platform.
- **Auto-k (elbow):** when `k=auto`, the API computes an elbow heuristic (inertia vs. k) and suggests a `k`. The dashboard visualizes this curve.
- **How:** FastAPI exposes endpoints; Streamlit renders clusters on a map and plots the elbow curve.

**Evidence:**
- `src/api/kmeans_airport_endpoints.py`
- `src/ml/auto_k_elbow.py`
- `src/ml/kmeans_airport_clusterer.py`
- `src/dashboard/pages/*clustering*.py`
- `src/dashboard/pages/*elbow*.py`
